talk_text:
Hmhmhm. I shared the Santa Power
from Mr. Christo to you, Sir Adell,
with my own powerup!

Inviting the Princess to the party
while dating other girls,
what a jerk. You! You cheating @#$%!

If word got out that my divination had made
for a lavish wedding in the new year,
my reputation would be further bolstered.

Besides, fortune-telling can make you happy
if it does come true, but even if it doesn't,
you can still feel excited and thrilled.
